

'''* Article / Book chapter: Common and commons in the contradictory dynamics between knowledge-based economy and cognitive capitalism. By Carlo Vercellone, Alfonso Giuliani. (From the Book: Cognitive Capitalism, Welfare and Labour). Routledge, 2020'''

